n and development concerns. To solidify this view, I would like to know:\n1. **Agent\u202f1**, do you have any information on Candidate\u202fC\u2019s sense of responsibility or his attitude toward professional development (e.g., willingness to pursue further training or education)?\n2. **Agent\u202f2**, do you have any additional data on Candidate\u202fD\u2019s stress\u2011handling capability or decision\u2011making speed that might offset his interpersonal weaknesses?\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
