iability** or his ability to handle stress and make decisions quickly?\n2. Does anyone know of any **positive teamwork or communication strengths for Candidate\u202fB** (beyond the noted uncooperativeness) or evidence of his decision\u2011making speed under pressure?\n3. Is there any data on **Candidate\u202fC\u2019s sense of responsibility** (e.g., taking ownership of tasks, accountability)?\n4. Does anyone have any **positive crew\u2011cooperation or communication observations for Candidate\u202fD**, or evidence of his stress handling and decision\u2011making speed?\nThese missing pieces will help us confirm whether Candidate\u202fC truly stands out or if another candidate may be more suitable for long\u2011distance operations.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
